                                                    <p>Wow, this game is fantastic! The combat mechanics are very fun. Unlike most FPS games where you just point and shoot, the primitive weapons in this game require you to fire at enemies and dodge from their attacks. Some weapons are very unique, so you learn how to set up your enemies to fall into your traps or corrupt them to help you fight. The enemies themselves have varied strengths and weaknesses, too. It's been fun trying to figure out how to bring down, say, a deadly oversized leopard-like Ravager versus a massive lightning-ball shooting Stormbird flying overhead.</p>
